OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC reverses plan to axe   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBBC Singers choir          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC has unveiled a plan that it    
OL,6, says "secures the future" of the BBC   
OL,7, Singers, its in-house chamber choir,   
OL,8, which had been threatened with closure.
OL,10,FLast year, the broadcaster caused an   
OL,11,Foutcry in the classical music world    
OL,12,Fwhen it decided to axe the group, with 
OL,13,Fthe loss of 20 jobs, to cut costs.     
OL,15,FHowever, the BBC has now said it will  
OL,16,Fcontinue to employ them, with no cuts  
OL,17,Fto their funding or posts.             
OL,19,FThey will form a new partnership with a
OL,20,Fvocal music education charity.         
